name: Domesticated Mix
description:
This model merges with multiple models. Try it out, experiment, and share the results! :)

Do you like what I do? You can buy me a food

You can also order the following LoRA models from the link above!

I recommend using the 2GB pruned version. The difference between full and this is minimal.

2GB pruned version ←Click here

This model is a merger:

  • YiffyMix2.2

  • Furryrock v2.0

  • FurtasticV2.0

  • Reliberate

Don't forget the negative embeddings! ←Click here

Thanks to sopenit494 for the negative embeddings

Also his model: FurtasticV2.0 - FurtasticV2.0 | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

Personally, I have them here:

D:\stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings
